## âš¡ Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- [Power BI Desktop](https://powerbi.microsoft.com/en-us/desktop/) (free) â€” required to open the `.pbix` file
- Microsoft Excel 2016+ or [LibreOffice Calc](https://www.libreoffice.org/) â€” to view the analysis workbook

### Steps

**1. Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/myntra-analytics-dashboard.git
cd myntra-analytics-dashboard
```

**2. Explore the Excel analysis**
```
Open: analysis/myntra_eda.xlsx
```
Navigate the sheets to follow the data cleaning steps and exploratory analysis.

**3. Open the Power BI dashboard**
```
Open: dashboard/Myntra_PowerBI_Dashboard.pbix
```
Power BI Desktop will load the full interactive report. Use the page tabs at the bottom to navigate between views.

**4. Refresh data (optional)**

If you update the source data, go to **Home â†’ Refresh** in Power BI Desktop to reload.

